ana is staying the same. How lure spells are supposed to give us exp in plane raids, i have no idea, or how it is even remotely fair for almost every other casting class to deal more damage, i.e. Magicians, whom, discounting their pets, actually deal MORE damage than a wizard at many intervals, lvl 34... etc. It just makes me angry at Verant, and depressed about being a Wizard.<br>
<br>
Apokriphos Moltenrain<br>
Level 49 Wizard, Zeb <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ualeolin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aleolin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/26/01 7:34:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=331.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Final Solution:: We have to spam Verant</span><hr size=1> Spamming has been tried and just doesn't help. Ever constantly begged something from a person only to find they are less likely to give you what you want if you are patient? I am so tired of Verant but I think if we were less forceful more would come our way. Force just turns people off, myself included. <br>
